    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>into the<strong> </strong>béchamel<strong> </strong>sauce, then add your <strong>Dijon mustard </strong>(not a mustard fan? Go easy!) and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Season generously with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong>, then add the <strong>cooked broccoli</strong> to the sauce and mix everything together – this is your <strong>broccoli cheese</strong></p>",
