    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, remove the <strong>baked</strong> <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong> from the oven and slice down the middle, leaving the ends intact</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Toss the<strong> salad </strong>with your<strong> balsamic vinegar </strong>and a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p>",
