    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>broccoli cheese</strong> over the <strong>baked sweet potato </strong>with the<strong> dressed salad </strong>to the side – these are your <strong>broccoli cheese-loaded baked sweet potato</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>herby panko </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) over the<strong> </strong>broccoli cheese-loaded baked sweet potato</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
